name: Projects
body:
## List of Projects

#### Projects undertaken by the club
1. [Crossword Quizzer] (https://github.com/WebAndCodingClub-IITGuwahati/Crossword-Quizzer)
2. [BotWars-Server] (https://github.com/WebAndCodingClub-IITGuwahati/BotWars-Server), [BotWars-Client] (https://github.com/WebAndCodingClub-IITGuwahati/BotWars-Client)
3. [Yearbook] (https://github.com/WebAndCodingClub-IITGuwahati/Yearbook)

#### Projects developed during Hackathons
1. [Hex] (https://github.com/WebAndCodingClub-IITGuwahati/Hex)
2. [SilentZio] (https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.iitg.call.manager&hl=en)
3. [IITG Bus Timings] (http://iitg-bus-timings.appspot.com/)
4. [Intranet Search] (https://github.com/WebAndCodingClub-IITGuwahati/IntranetSearch)
5. [GDSync] (https://github.com/rovinbhandari/GDSync)
6. [Quora Read Later] (https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/quora-read-later/nialelmigpbhicbheglinidbfpgkmana)
7. Webmail notification Chrome extension (Chrome webstore link to be added)
8. [AutoBright] (https://github.com/harshg0910/AutoBright)

#### Student driven projects
1. [IIT Guwahati Bus Timings (Android App)] (https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kadtech.xlab.bustiming&hl=en)
2. [Gesture Force] (https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ajaykumar.sense) 
3. [IITG Transparent Proxy] (https://github.com/suhailsherif/IITG-Transparent-Proxy)
4. [Pycurl-Downloader] (https://github.com/rajatkhanduja/PyCurl-Downloader)
5. [JasmineSDK] (https://github.com/snagarohit/jasminesdk)
